name: UnofficialUniversalStudiosHollywood
0:
”Alexa, what is the wait time for Jurassic World The Ride?”
”Alexa, ask Universal Hollywood the operating hours for tomorrow?”
”Alexa, launch Universal Hollywood to know if the park is busy today”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: universal hollywood
des: Willing to go to Universal Hollywood this week-end and do not know the operating hours, ask me. If you are in the park, you can also ask me for the current wait times for your favorite rides. Discover if the park is busy today.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
